# Laptop: hybrid — AMD iGPU primary (battery life), NVIDIA dGPU for offload.
#
# Deliberately NO global NVIDIA env vars here: they would push rendering and
# VA-API onto the dGPU and kill battery. Run heavy apps on the dGPU with:
#   prime-run <app>

# If Hyprland picks the dGPU instead of the AMD iGPU, pin the iGPU first.
# Verify card numbering with: ls -l /dev/dri/by-path/
# env = AQ_DRM_DEVICES,/dev/dri/card0:/dev/dri/card1
